        <div onclick="setWorldPage(0)" id="wtab-0" style="flex-shrink:0;padding:5px 14px;border-radius:20px;font-size:11px;font-weight:600;cursor:pointer;border:1.5px solid rgba(192,132,252,.6);background:rgba(192,132,252,.15);color:#c084fc;transition:all .2s">вЪФпЄП еЉВзХМеЙѓжЬђ</div>
        <div onclick="setWorldPage(1)" id="wtab-1" style="flex-shrink:0;padding:5px 14px;border-radius:20px;font-size:11px;cursor:pointer;border:1px solid var(--bdr);background:transparent;color:var(--dim);transition:all .2s">вЪФпЄП зЂЮжКАеЬЇ</div>
        <div style="flex:1"></div>
        <div onclick="openAbyssShop()" style="flex-shrink:0;font-size:10px;padding:4px 10px;border-radius:6px;border:1px solid rgba(201,162,39,.4);color:var(--gl);cursor:pointer;background:rgba(201,162,39,.08)">рЯЫТ еХЖеЇЧ</div>
